Suggested-by: Laurent Pinchart <laurent.pinchart@ideasonboard.com>
Tested-by: Jacopo Mondi <jacopo+renesas@jmondi.org>
Signed-off-by: Akinobu Mita <akinobu.mita@gmail.com>
